data.description: Discover coastal paradise in this 3 bedrooms , 2bath,  canal home in Indian Harbour Beach, Florida. A beacon of tranquility, the  open-concept interior bathes in natural light, seamlessly connecting to a screened patio overlooking the canal. Modern kitchen amenities make cooking a breeze. Nestled near Gleason Park for a amazing walk or walking your dog in the park and pristine beaches, it offers the perfect blend of convenience and relaxation. The master suite provides a serene retreat, while the backyard boasts a private space for your enjoyment. Embrace the laid-back Florida lifestyle in this meticulously designed home, offering a seamless blend of comfort, and coastal charm.
